game.name: Equestria Girls Graduation Party
game.description:
Today the beautiful three princesses Apple Jack, Rainbow and Twilight look pretty excited to join the graduation ball at their college! Their excitement is at the highest level since they are going to graduate from their college. But, a problem has made them worry a bit. They do not have a proper idea what to wear to look fabulous on their big day. Join Equestria Girls Graduation Party Game and help the three princesses to pick up a nice outfit and solve their problem!
Browse through their wider collection of outfits and assist the princesses to get the super gorgeous graduation looks in this brand new dressing game for girls! These three princesses are the best friends and they do want to miss any event when they join together. Choose from an extensive variety of robes, bachelor caps and a pair of matching shoes! They trust on your fashion designer skills, so do your best to design a wonderful graduation outfit for each of the lovely princesses. 
It is a big day in their lives when they are going to become the university graduates. So, mix and match as many options as you can to guide them to pick up the nice outfit and make them university graduation event worth remembering. Their wardrobe will show you a fabulous range of colorful outfits, exclusive hairstyles, a pair of matching shoes and earrings and hats. Good luck to help them pick up the nice outfits to prepare graduation party in the optimum possible way!
